rather rosy picture of it,

00:55:52.680 --> 00:55:55.110
is just, you know, burley
guys working it out,

00:55:55.110 --> 00:55:58.140
so to speak, and also,

00:55:59.910 --> 00:56:02.360
the religious area too,

00:56:02.360 --> 00:56:04.980
because there's a mix of, you know,

